uence modeling, DebatePeer transforms the ReviewCritique dataset from a passive evaluation corpus into an active simulation engine for scientific reasoning. We release the framework with configurable debate templates, agent initialization pipelines, and visualization dashboards for analyzing discourse dynamics. This work redefines LLM benchmarking in peer review—not as a one-shot judgment task, but as a collaborative, truth-seeking process—thereby advancing the development of LLMs capable of genuine scientific dialogue.",
